[l] Endlich hat die Wissenschaft herausgefunden, wieso Maenner bei Scrabble-Tournieren staerker als Frauen spielen. Die Antwort:Men generally outperform women in Scrabble tournaments because female competitors are less willing to spend their time improving a largely pointless skill, according to new research.Scientists found male players spend their time practising anagrams and analysing the game, whereas women are more likely to play the game as a hobby.
